            <h5>GOAL</h5>
            <br>
            <p>
                The goal of the guild is to clear all available raid tiers, as fast as possible within our 1-2 raiding days.
                We put a big focus on structure and dedication - we are not a hardcore guild in terms of hours played, but we take a serious approach to our raids and time we spend together as a guild.
            </p>
        </div>
