            <h5>﻿LOOT RULES</h5>
            <p>
                The guild is running with a "DKP'like" system called EPGP (Effort Points/Gear Points). The system is based on a priority system that ranks players based on gear received and attendance. On top we have a completely custom price list, were each GP price is based on the stat weight of each class. On top of that we will be running with a soft priority system that will make sure that the right classes get the correct items. You can find an example of the BWL price list here https://www.vanguard-guild.com/bwl-gp.
            </p>
            <p>
                During some raids some members might end up on standby. Players on standby will receive 100% effort points as long as they stay active.
            </p>
            <p>
                Decay is happening after each Sunday raid. This will reduce everybody's EP and GP by 10% and will be rolled out across ALL players. This is to encourage people to grab items as they will essentially get a 10% discount on the price when the decay occurs.
            </p>
            <p>
                <b>Recruit can only obtain gear if no raider wants the item, but will still receive Effort Points when attending raids.</b>
            </p>
